        <text>
            <body>
                  <p>
                        <hi rend="background(yellow)">Acte mentionné : Fontaines-en-Duesmois -
                            Emorots. II</hi>
                    </p>
                    <p>Ego <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324577" xml:id="d1e133060" corresp="Hugues III, duc de Bourgogne (1162-1192)">dux <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325098" xml:id="d1e133062" corresp="Bourgogne">Burgundie</placeName>,
                            Hugo</persName>, presentibus et futuris notum facio quod <persName key="d1e12362" xml:id="d1e133066">Pontius, dominus <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324442" xml:id="d1e133068" corresp="Duesme (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Duismi</placeName>
                        </persName>, et uxor ejus, <persName key="d1e12368" xml:id="d1e133071">filia
                                <persName key="d1e12374" xml:id="d1e133073">Willermi <lb n="2" /> de
                                    <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324442" xml:id="d1e133077" corresp="Duesme (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Duismo</placeName>
                            </persName>
                        </persName>, laudaverunt donum et elemosinam quam fecerunt ecclesie <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e133080" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName>
                        <persName key="d1e12380" xml:id="d1e133082">Savaricus</persName> et
                            <persName key="d1e12386" xml:id="d1e133085">Andreas</persName> et
                            <persName key="d1e12392" xml:id="d1e133089">Herveius</persName>, fratres
                            <lb n="3" /> de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324452" xml:id="d1e133094" corresp="Fontaines-en-Duesmois (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Fontanis</placeName>, de casamento suo : omnes scilicet aasentias
                        terrarum suarum de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324452" xml:id="d1e133097" corresp="Fontaines-en-Duesmois (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Fontanis</placeName> in bosco et in plano et in aquis <lb n="4" /> suis
                        et pasturas omnibus animalibus, pastionem porcis et carreriam trium tesiarum
                        per medium pratorum ad riveriam. <lb n="5" /> Concesserunt et laudaverunt
                        divisionem quam fecerunt homines <app>
                            <lem wit="#A">monacorum</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#B">monachorum</rdg>
                        </app> inter finagia de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324452" xml:id="d1e133111" corresp="Fontaines-en-Duesmois (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Fontanis</placeName> et de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324375" xml:id="d1e133114" corresp="Verdonnet (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Ver<lb n="6" break="no" />dennaco</placeName> et de
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324449" xml:id="d1e133119" corresp="Étormay (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">
                            <foreign>Estormer</foreign>
                        </placeName>. <app>
                            <lem wit="#A">
                                <sic>Granntaverunt</sic>
                            </lem>
                            <rdg wit="#B">grantaverunt</rdg>
                        </app> quoque quod usagia que homines sui in terris monachorum se habere
                        dicebant <lb n="7" /> eos in pace guerpire facerent. Hec omnia laudavit
                            <persName key="d1e12399" xml:id="d1e133133">Pontius</persName> et uxor
                        ejus et cetera omnia que continentur in carta de his ple<lb n="8" break="no" />nius facta et <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324645" xml:id="d1e133138" corresp="Étienne II, évêque d'Autun (1171-1189)">Eduensis
                            episcopi</persName> sigillo signata. Unde testes sunt <persName key="d1e12405" xml:id="d1e133141">Lambertus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324432" xml:id="d1e133143" corresp="Conforgien (Côte-d'Or, Arnay-le-Duc)">
                                <foreign>
                                    <app>
                                        <lem wit="#A">Cofergen</lem>
                                        <rdg wit="#B">Corfergen</rdg>
                                    </app>
                                </foreign>
                            </placeName>
                        </persName> et <persName key="d1e12411" xml:id="d1e133151">Bernardus</persName> frater ejus, <persName key="d1e12417" xml:id="d1e133154">Girar<lb n="9" break="no" />dus
                                <addName>Pilosus</addName>
                        </persName> et <persName key="d1e12423" xml:id="d1e133162">Wiardus</persName> filius ejus, <persName key="d1e12429" xml:id="d1e133165">
                            <app>
                                <lem wit="#A">Wiardus</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B">Viardus</rdg>
                            </app> de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325029" xml:id="d1e133172" corresp="Seneveii">Seneveio</placeName>
                        </persName> et <persName key="d1e12436" xml:id="d1e133175">Johannes</persName> frater ejus. Ego quoque hoc testor et ne qua hinc
                        in posterum <lb n="10" /> oriatur querela, presentem cartam sigilli mei
                        appensione confirmo.</p>
                
